               <msContents>
                  <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
                  <msItem>
                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_107027">Clapcote</placeName>.
                             
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Alan</forename> of <surname>Goldeburghe</surname>
                        </persName> grants to <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Heron</surname>
                        </persName>, prior &amp;c. of <orgName key="org_107004">W<supplied>allingford</supplied>
                        </orgName> 7½ acres of arable land in <placeName key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName>, and an acre of meadow, viz.: ½ acre at <placeName type="minor">Hongerhulle</placeName>, ½ acre in le <placeName type="minor">Flexlonde</placeName>, above <placeName type="minor">le Pende</placeName>, 2 acres in <placeName type="minor">Algarsforlong</placeName>, 1 acre at <placeName type="minor">la Grodelonde</placeName>, above <placeName type="minor">Algarsforlong</placeName>, ½ acre near the <placeName type="minor">Shillingford road</placeName>, 1 acre at <placeName type="minor">Gondricheshulle</placeName>, 1 acre in <placeName type="minor">Middelforlong</placeName> (½ acre of which reaches la <placeName type="minor">Rysshepathe</placeName>), ½ acre not specified, ½ acre in the common meadow ’prout sors condonet annuatim in sorte <persName>
                           <forename>Alicie</forename> 
                           <surname>Reynaudyn</surname>
                        </persName>’, ½ acre similarly ’in sorte <forename>
                           <forename>Ricardi</forename> de <surname>Louches</surname>
                        </forename>’. 
                            Witnesses: <!--[as in no 77, without Nicholas le coupere]-->
                            <supplied>
                           <persName>
                              <forename>Richard</forename> 
                              <surname>Moryn</surname>, mayor</persName>,
                                <persName>
                              <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Louches</surname>
                           </persName>, 
                                <persName>
                              <forename>Gilbert</forename> du <surname>Char</surname>
                           </persName>,
                                <persName>
                              <forename>Thomas</forename> 
                              <surname>Alayn</surname>
                           </persName>,
                                <persName>
                              <forename>Walter</forename> 
                              <surname>Crips</surname>
                           </persName>, 
                                <persName>
                              <forename>Thomas</forename> of <surname>Oterburne</surname>
                           </persName>,
                                <persName>
                              <forename>William</forename> 
                              <surname>Knight</surname>, clerk</persName>. </supplied>.
                            Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName>.
                            <origDate when="1334-03-12"><!--Same date.-->
                           <supplied>12 March 1334.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
                        </p>
